This period marks a time where your sense of responsibility and duty will be at the forefront. You will make many important decisions and you will bind yourself to them and stand behind them. This is the best cycle to consider business partnerships, purchasing a home or getting married. Partnerships formed during this period are more likely to succeed than at any other point in your life. You will find yourself feeling loved and appreciated and any and all joint ventures upon which you embark will be successful. You will also find that those around you support you unwaveringly and you will live in a manner that makes you deserving of it. Hidden talents are likely to surface during this period as well.
